    <h3><%=image_tag('kitty.jpg', alt: "Home", width:25) %> What is CrowdKitty?</h3>
    <h6>CrowdKitty is an innovative crowdfunding platform that provides a way for people to join forces and make ideas happen.</h6>
    <p>Since 2015, thousands of people have backed hundreds of projects with the aim of trying to bring big dreams to life that will better their local community. We have a simple mission: to empower everyone to change the world, one idea at a time. Kathryn, Keith, and Chae started CrowdKitty in order to revolutionize the ability of ordinary people to fund worthy projects that can help make local communities better.</p>

    <h5><%=image_tag('kitty.jpg', alt: "Home", width:25) %> Who are we?</h5>
